* ================================================================
* CONDUCTOR AND LOAD SPICE MODELS
* Conductor and Load 
* ================================================================
* File: conductor_load.lib
* Description: Library for conductor and load elements
* ================================================================

* ================================================================
* CONDUCTOR - CONDUCTANCE ELEMENT
* ================================================================
* A conductor is the reciprocal of resistance
* Conductance G = 1/R (measured in Siemens, S)
* ================================================================
.SUBCKT CONDUCTOR NP NM PARAMS: G=1
* R = 1/G
R_COND  NP NM  {1/G}
.ENDS CONDUCTOR

* ================================================================
* LOAD Power 
* ================================================================
* A load element represents a device that consumes power
* It can be modeled  power load
* Symbol: power load
* Parameters:  P (power)
* ================================================================

.SUBCKT LOAD_Power NP NM PARAMS: P=5W
* Behavioral model for  power load
* I = P / V
B_LOAD  NP NM  I={P/V(NP,NM)}
.ENDS LOAD_Power


